{"id":274959,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/01/维权网-临沂拆迁受害人向彭丽媛求助，刘国慧被/","date":"2013-01-17T08:45:43Z","modified":"2013-01-17T08:45:43Z","title":"维权网 | 临沂拆迁受害人向彭丽媛求助，刘国慧被抓后下落不明（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员张宁宁报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">16</span><span>日早</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>点</span><span>许，山东省临沂拆迁受害人刘国慧、秦玉玲、魏兰玉（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">62</span><span>岁）、王汝兰（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">71</span><span>岁）、杨自娥、卢秋梅等人到解放军艺术学院门口，打出“彭丽媛，老乡求见你”的标语。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>六位暴力拆迁受害人曾经向全国政协委员彭丽媛写信，反映临沂市政府暴力强拆民房的恶性事件，以及当地法院不依法立案，或者立案后久拖不审等违法行为。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>临沂市拆迁受害人得知彭丽媛已收到信后，于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">16</span><span>日</span><span>赶到北京，希望与山东老乡面谈。她们没有见到彭丽媛，却被北京大钟寺派出所扣押。随后，山东省驻京办带领黑保安将她们押回临沂市，关押在兰山区治安大队，由兰山区国保刘洪义亲自审讯。刘国慧的电话一直关机，目前情况不明。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>临沂市拆迁受害人：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>秦玉玲：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">15653990650</span></div>\n<div><span>杨自娥：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13854929904</span></div>\n<div><span>王汝兰：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">15969912992</span></div>\n<div><span>魏兰玉：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13954927979</span></div>\n<div><span>卢秋梅：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13082668722</span></div>\n<div><span>刘国慧：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">15564215129</span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-15FFcgetblk/UPegDD-kZTI/AAAAAAAAZMU/eJWYJv4En6k/s1600/%E5%88%98%E5%9B%BD%E8%BE%89.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"232\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-15FFcgetblk/UPegDD-kZTI/AAAAAAAAZMU/eJWYJv4En6k/s320/%E5%88%98%E5%9B%BD%E8%BE%89.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时